divs: Sighting Detailsi was preparing to cook on my grill and it was very cloudy no stars in the sky, i seen a bright oval light shoot across the sky under the clouds like a shooting star, but of course it couldn't have been that... it was way to slow also to be a shooting star but faster than a jet and no sound when it came across the sky.
Summary: standing outside cloudy night no stars and shot across the sky
